Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Cucumber
results.story: The Salehe Bembury x Crocs Pollex Clog ‘Green’ applies a monochrome finish to a reworked version of the Classic Clog. Bembury covers the molded foam build in concave ridges that resemble the footwear designer’s signature fingerprint motif. The textured pattern extends to the outsole for multi-directional traction, while targeted ventilation ports in the upper provide enhanced breathability. A removable heel strap features dual Crocs and Salehe Bembury branding.

results.name: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Menemsha
results.story: Conceived in partnership with the acclaimed footwear designer, the Salehe Bembury x Crocs Pollex Clog ‘Brown’ delivers a remixed version of the Classic Clog silhouette. A dark taupe hue floods the reconstructed foam build, highlighted by a series of concave ridges that recall Bembury’s signature fingerprint motif. Ventilation ports are meant to align with high-heat areas of the foot for targeted ventilation. Dual Crocs and Salehe Bembury branding is embossed on the removable heel strap.

results.name: Crocs Classic Clog Nightmare Before Christmas
results.story: The Disney x Crocs Classic Clog ‘The Nightmare Before Christmas’ pays homage to the 1993 stop-motion animated film conceived by Tim Burton. The slip-on is built with black Croslite foam, entirely covered in greyscale graphics that depict Jack Skellington’s likeness. The neutral color scheme is disrupted by yellow logo buttons on the pivoting heel strap. The clogs come with a set of glow-in-the-dark Jibbitz charms, including an oversized Jack Skellington head and ‘The Nightmare Before Christmas’ branding.

Crocs Classic Clog x thisisneverthat x Realtree Multi
results.story: The thisisneverthat x Realtree x Crocs Classic Clog ‘Edge Camo’ updates the slip-on silhouette with an all-over print designed for outdoor adventures. Rendered in Walnut brown with green and orange accents, the Realtree Edge camo pattern is accompanied by thisisneverthat branding throughout. The Korean streetwear brand’s logo makes repeat appearances via an accompanying set of Jibbitz charms. The clog itself is built with lightweight Croslite foam and features a pivoting heel strap and a series of ventilation ports along the vamp and forefoot.

results.name: Space Jam x Classic Clogs 'Tune Squad'
results.story: Celebrating the release of ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy,’ the Crocs Classic Clog ‘Tune Squad’ features a black Croslite foam upper with contrasting orange and royal blue accents on the adjustable turbo heel strap. Atop the vamp, concentric orange and yellow circles give the nod to classic Looney Tunes iconography. The graphic print is complemented by a set of Jibbitz charms that depict a basketball and the Tune Squad and Space Jam logos. Underfoot, a lugged outsole provides durable traction on multiple surfaces.

results.name: Crocs Classic All-Terrain Clog Space Jam Black Purple
results.story: The Space Jam x Crocs Classic Clog ‘A New Legacy’ showcases a unique design inspired by LeBron James’ live action/animated blockbuster. A gradient blend of violet and blue is applied to the Croslite foam upper, featuring circuit board graphics that nod to the film’s villainous AI. The all-terrain clog is equipped with ventilation ports, an adjustable turbo heel strap and a durable lugged outsole. Accompanying Jibbitz charms include a basketball and Tune Squad and Space Jam logos.

results.name: Crocs Classic Sandal Diplo Take a Walk on the Weird Side
results.story: The Diplo x Crocs Classic Sandal 2 ‘Take a Walk on the Weird Side’ updates the slip-on silhouette with a psychedelic design, courtesy of the influential producer and DJ. The lightweight sandal, built with the same Croslite foam construction as the Classic Clog, features a swirling mix of blue, pink and yellow hues on the two upper straps and midsole. An accompanying set of eight glow-in-the-dark Jibbitz charms allow for a custom look.

results.name: Crocs Classic Clog Diplo Take a Walk on the Weird Side
results.story: Designed in partnership with the Grammy Award-winning producer and DJ, the Diplo x Crocs Classic Clog ‘Take a Walk on the Weird Side’ dresses the foam slip-on in a vibrant blend of blue, pink and yellow hues. The psychedelic swirling-paint design is complemented by a multicolor set of mushroom Jibbitz charms that glow in the dark. Standard features include ventilation ports for improved breathability and a pivoting heel strap for a secure fit.

results.name: Crocs Classic Hiker Peace Out Green
Palace x Classic Clog 'Tan Camo'
results.story: The Palace x Crocs Classic Clog ‘Tan Camo’ delivers the London skate brand’s take on the flexible slip-on silhouette. A desert camouflage print floods the exterior of the Croslite foam build, featuring breathable ventilation ports and a pivoting heel strap for a secure fit. Palace’s signature triangle logo is stamped in yellow on the contoured footbed. Additional branding elements take the form of eleven Jibbitz charms that accompany the limited-edition release.

results.name: Classic Hiker Clog 'Peace Out - Multi Black'
Crocs Classic Clog Justin Bieber with drew house 2 Lavender
results.story: Representing collaboration no. 2 with the high-profile musician, the Justin Bieber x Crocs Classic Clog ‘Drew House’ features a standard Croslite foam build in a soft lavender finish. Large ventilation ports throughout the forefoot yield breathable comfort, while a wraparound heel strap provides a secure fit. The clogs are packaged with oversized Jibbitz charms inspired by characters from the Drew House community, along with a pair of white Drew House socks.

Crocs Duet Max 2 Post Malone Pink
Crocs Classic Lined Clog Luke Combs Skully
results.story: Designed in partnership with the country music singer-songwriter, the Luke Combs x Crocs Classic Lined Clog ‘Skully’ features a white foam exterior and a black sherpa lining for added comfort and warmth. Combs’ signature Skully graphic adorns the vamp, while five unique Jibbitz charms — including the musician’s Gibson guitar, a pair of his cowboy boots and a bone for his puppy Jojo — offer a range of customization opportunities.

results.name: Crocs Classic Clog Nicole McLaughlin
results.story: Conceptualized in partnership with the Boston-based designer, the Nicole McLaughlin x Crocs Classic Clog ‘Survival Kit’ delivers a campsite-ready take on the slip-on silhouette. The standard Clog, featuring black foam construction with ventilation ports and customizable Jibbitz charms, adds a two-tone gaiter-like shroud, secured with drawstring closure and equipped with a zippered pouch. The heel strap is outfitted with a working compass and light for outdoor adventures.

results.name: Crocs Classic Clog Bieber with drew house
results.story: Made in collaboration with the Canadian singer/songwriter, the Justin Bieber x Crocs Classic Clog ‘Drew’ features a monochromatic yellow finish in a nod to the former’s fashion brand, Drew House. The slip-on is built with Croslite foam and appointed with standard Classic Clog details, including ventilation ports and a pivoting heel strap for a secure fit. Eight unique Jibbitz charms allow for a customized look.

results.name: Daily Paper x Classic Clog 'Green Camo'
Bad Bunny x Classic Clog 'Glow In The Dark'
Crocs Classic Clog Grateful Dead x Chinatown Market
results.story: The Grateful Dead x Chinatown Market x Crocs Clog ‘Tie Dye’ is taken from a larger collaboration between the legendary San Francisco jam band and LA-based streetwear brand. Their take on the classic Crocs slip-on features a psychedelic tie-dye print with removable 3D Jibbitz charms depicting the Dead’s signature dancing bears. Dual Chinatown Market and Grateful Dead branding adorns the clog’s heel strap and footbed.

results.name: Crocs Classic Clog KFC
results.story: Made in collaboration with the fast food chain, the KFC x Crocs Classic Clog ‘Fried Chicken Print’ celebrates the Colonel’s original recipe with a playful design. Not only is the perforated upper covered in an all-over fried chicken print, but the clogs come with two Jibbitz charms made to resemble — and smell —like actual drumsticks. The midsole is finished in the same red and white stripes that adorn a KFC bucket, accented with Colonel Sanders’ likeness on the right heel.

results.name: Crocs Classic Bootlegger Slide Luke Combs Black
Post Malone x Duet Max Clog 'Blue Camo'
results.story: Designed in collaboration with the genre-crossing American rapper, the Post Malone x Duet Max Clog 'Blue Camo' sits on a rugged lug outsole for durable traction. Up top, the slip-on build is finished in a unique black and blue camo pattern that extends to the midsole. Adjustable straps at the heel and midfoot deliver a secure fit, while ventilation ports throughout the vamp are good for breathable comfort.

results.name: Crocs Duet Max Clog Post Malone
results.story: Made in collaboration with the genre-blending American rapper, the Post Malone x Crocs Duet Max Clog ‘Blue Camo’ features a subtle all-over print on both the upper and sole unit. The slip-on build features airy ventilation holes across the vamp for increased airflow, while an adjustable dual strap system is good for a custom fit. A Croslite foam footbed offers contoured comfort. Underfoot, flex grooves on the outsole deliver a smooth ride.

Crocs Classic Clog Luke Combs Realtree Camo
Crocs Classic Clog Takashi Murakami x ComplexCon
results.story: Released exclusively at ComplexCon in November 2019, Takashi Murakami's interpretation of the Crocs Clog is inspired by his psychedelic illustration style. The sandal arrives draped in multi-color camouflage with a teddy bear Jibbitz charm and the Japanese artist's smiling daisy on the adjustable slingback strap. A special graphic on the insole and durable rubber outsole complete the collaborative design.

results.name: Pleasures x Clog 'Utopia Dystopia'
results.story: Unveiled in August 2019, the Pleasures x Crocs Clog 'Utopia Dystopia' takes inspiration from subjects of customization within youth subculture like leather jackets and backpacks. The sandal's black upper is embellished with Jibbitz charms showcasing motifs from the label’s archive. Other graphic elements include branding along the slingback strap and 'SOMEWHERE BETWEEN UTOPIA AND DYSTOPIA' in white lettering around the midsole.

results.name: Chinatown Market x Clog 'Tie Dye Smiley'
results.story: For their second collaboration in July 2019, Chinatown Market remixed the classic Crocs clog to honor American iconography. The sandal is constructed of a bright Croslite synthetic material and features a tie-dye print on the vamp and heel and two oversized Smiley Jibbitz charms allowing for customization. The label's whimsical spirit is translated via a text graphic printed on the footbed and branded slingback strap.

results.name: Crocs Classic Clog Barneys New York XO Punk Denim
Post Malone x Clog 'Postyco Green' Australia Exclusive
results.story: To celebrate the rapper's Australian tour, the Post Malone x Crocs Clog 'Postyco Green' was released exclusively in the country in May 2019. The sandal is covered in a tropical rainforest graphic and embellished with three interchangeable Jibbitz charms on each foot. Malone's logo is printed on the heel. Classic features include a pivoting strap, ventilation ports at the toe box and a rubber outsole.

results.name: Chinatown Market x Clog 'Grass Turf'
results.story: Crocs worked alongside Los Angeles-based streetwear brand Chinatown Market for the uniquely designed Chinatown Market x Clog 'Grass Turf' shoe. Released in January 2019, the slip-on clog is wrapped in a soft turf textile that covers the upper and insole. Accented with contrast black trimmings, the unisex shoe is completed with Chinatown Market branding along the crossfoot bar and hinges to complete the playful look.

results.name: Crocs Dimitri Clog Post Malone Barbed Wire
results.story: Crocs invited Post Malone to put his stamp on the Classic Clog in December 2018. The result is this special ‘Barbed Wire’ iteration that sees the slip-on’s rubber upper dipped in yellow and accentuated by a barbed wire graphic and six Post Malone-themed Jibbitz that can be attached to the shoe’s perforations.

results.name: Crocs Dimitri Clog Post Malone
results.story: An unexpected collaboration with rapper Post Malone and shoe brand Crocs results in the bright and bold Post Malone x Crocs Clog 'Dimitri' shoe. Released in November 2018 as part of Crocs' 'Come As You Are' campaign, the recognizable slip-on design incorporates an allover baby devil face motif and six removable 'Jibbitz' charms—including Post Malone’s ‘Stay Away’ tattoo and the rapper’s 'Posty Co' logo. A secured ankle strap and ventilation ports on the toe box complete the look.
